### ===== LEGACY EXPORT ENDPOINT (BACKWARD COMPATIBILITY) =====

### Legacy: Export all assets as JSON (GET endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/export/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Legacy: Export folder assets as JSON (GET endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets/export/json?assetGroupId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

